    • Uses of ISensorDataListener in at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.network

      Classes in at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.network that implement ISensorDataListener 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ServerConnection
      This class is used to communicate with a TCP-Server via a TCP-connection and is able to send sensor-data to the server and receive control-data from the server to control the car.
      Listeners are able to register themselves with the ServerConnection to get updated about sending and receiving data as well as connection updates.

      Creates a new SensorDataListener with the given parameters and adds it to RMCSComponentManager.dataListeners, unless a SensorDataListener with the given ISensorDataListener is already in RMCSComponentManager.dataListeners, in which case the passed EDataTypes are merely added to the list of EDataTypes of the SensorDataListener that contains the passed ISensorDataListener.
